headline: AI capex is finally showing up in the real economy
summary: Opening Bid Unfiltered is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, YouTube, or wherever you get your podcasts. AI spending is finally hitting the GDP, not just stock tickers. On Opening Bid Unfiltered, Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi sits down with Gargi Chaudhuri, Head of iShares Investment Strategy Americas at BlackRock, to unpack how AI investments drive growth through software and intellectual property. They explore how this shift could shape future earnings beyond semiconductors and what it means for the labor market, immigration, and productivity. This is where AI meets the real economy. Listen on your favorite podcast platform or watch on our website for full episodes of Opening Bid Unfiltered. This post was written by Langston Sessoms, producer for Opening Bid Unfiltered.
